## Configuring

The Qovery configuration file is placed in:

```text
/usr/local/etc/qovery/qovery.toml
```

A full spec is located at `/usr/local/etc/qovery/qovery.spec.toml` and examples
are located in `/usr/local/etc/qovery/examples/*`. You can learn more about
configuring Qovery in the [Configuration][docs.configuration] section.

