## Uninstalling

```bash
brew remove qovery
```

## Updating

```bash
brew update && brew upgrade qovery
```

## Package

### Architectures

Qovery's Homebrew packages only support the X86_64 arhcitecture.

### Versions

Historical Qovery versions can be found in the [releases][urls.qovery_releases].
Once you've found the version you'd like to install you can specify it with:

```bash
brew install qovery@X.X.X
```

Due to limitations of Homebrew, Qovery cannot pin specific major or minor
versions. If this is a requirement, then we recommend installing Qovery
directly [from an archive][docs.manual.from-archives].

